tafsir[4]{c,v,t}:
  106,1,"Sabu woowde Quraysi en e aadorde …ìe."
  106,2,"…óatngal dabbunde faade Yaman e cee…óu faade Saam tawa ho…ìe kisi."
  106,3,"Yo …ìe ndew jom ndu suudu hormaandu Kanko tan, Oon newnan…óo …ìe ngal …óatngal, woto …ìe ndenndi Mbo e go…ó…óo."
  106,4,"Oon √±ammin…óo …ìe saanga heege, o hoolni…ìe e kulol, ko laati e …ìer…óe arab teddinde suudu hormaandu ndu e teddinde ho…ó…ìe heen."
